Chantelle Kotze, Senior Deputy Editor at Mining Review Africa, chats to the winner of the Mining Indaba Young Leaders Competition, Olebogeng Sentsho, CEO of Simba Mgodi Fund about her novel mining fund. You can view all of our Mining Indaba 2019 videos here Simba Mgodi is an incubation fund designed to support emerging entrepreneurs in mining and mining services. It offers asset, contract and capital finance for businesses active in the mining industry. As the mining industry approaches its next super cycle, the board of directors at The Simba Mgodi Mining Fund have resolved to employ an innovative set of investment strategies designed to meet the diverse needs of its clients.